## Add the required schema to create requests

The curl body includes:

```json
"schemas": [
  "urn:pingidentity:schemas:partners-BE-AP74737:1.0"
]
```

Make sure your create mapper includes it:

```java
private static final String RESOURCE_SCHEMA =
        "urn:pingidentity:schemas:partners-BE-AP74737:1.0";

public PartnersBEAP74737Get200ResponseResourcesInner toPingUser(
        UserEntity user
) {
    PartnersBEAP74737Get200ResponseResourcesInner request =
            new PartnersBEAP74737Get200ResponseResourcesInner();

    request.setSchemas(Set.of(RESOURCE_SCHEMA));
    request.setCn(user.getUserId());
    request.setMail(user.getEmail());
    request.setGivenName(user.getFirstName());
    request.setMobile(user.getPhoneNumber());
    request.setSn(user.getLastName());
    request.setStatus(mapStatus(user.getStatus()));

    return request;
}
```

